&lt;p&gt;This post is for a Band 5 Occupational Therapist on a fixed term contract (Oct 2020 to March 2021) working full time hours within our Community Teams across North and East Cornwall and will be based in Carew House, Bodmin and Liskeard Hospital respectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced, caring, motivated OT to join and support our Community Teams. You should be flexible, and possess commitment to team working, and innovative delivery of excellent standards of care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should also have an understanding of the changing climate of care delivery in the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
